The Second Book of Hope

Tommi Musturi

Bries, 2007, 48 pages

The Books of Hope is a story of one good life and few deaths. To be more exact it is a story of an elderly couple who take a look back in their life.

This is a five book series originally published independently in Finnish by Tommi Musturi. To date I believe only the first three have been published in English and I only have the first two ready to share at the moment.
